{"tid":228591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向警署掟磚被問因由    無業青年：唔知呀我都","createTime":"2017-05-04T04:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T05:15:24.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d4800a27eaa6f82d5a2771901881becdaaf5222","tid":228591,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170504/large/1493870337_ffb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170504%2Flarge%2F1493870337_ffb0.jpg&h=be47b2dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n25歲無業青年於今年3月21日，無故向秀茂坪警署掟磚，輕微損壞警署玻璃牆。他今在觀塘法院承認一項刑事損壞罪，裁判官問他為何犯案，他只回答：唔知呀我都。」裁判官將他還柙，等候索取精神及心理科等4份報告，本月18日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n依靠家人接濟的被告伍潤雄，過往有3次案底，其中與毒品有關，裁判官遂下令為被告索取戒毒所、心理科、精神科及背景報告。伍當日犯案後逃走，但犯案過程被警員目擊，警員同日稍後於順利邨附近將被告拘捕。"},{"pid":"4a0fc409b2183aaf33efc38ac554295cd4fe639e","tid":228591,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:22:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"617445119ca9fd57537eb53b4d141ea10fa6124b","tid":228591,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16b4de45d867ed8615350fc5cbaca9ad1259638","tid":228591,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"479ea524c6c4be6fcaf0b7c0a6757e8fafc77d54","tid":228591,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"心諗做乜鳩<br />\n不如係門口屙篤屎算啦<br />\n有乜用？點解唔做更偉大既事"},{"pid":"6b6d4c8a0a67963da3c3ab629b126f7a2d5460fe","tid":228591,"uid":99175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢醒呀 無特定目標不涉刑事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n警署=/=毀損罪既特定目標?"},{"pid":"4bea2939dc7429910c59feaa2e70b92d38080ff2","tid":228591,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,